Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.99,0:01:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敖德薩作戰前善戰的White Base\N也已經破爛不堪而迫降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.21,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然ZION軍的戰鬥部隊一時撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.67,0:02:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但全然不知何時會再來襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.86,0:02:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『瑪吉露達救出作戰』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得好像在右邊的那個才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.51,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以試試引擎的線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.04,0:02:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不太適合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果還修不好，我的紙快用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，你再這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別人會把你當作沒用的人呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...機器的壓力正常嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣？有代替品嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行呢！我試過了很多種了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果敵人現在來便糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.31,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們說過會支持我們的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！關於補給品...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，布萊特在找你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，布萊特在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，有事找我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.12,0:03:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你暫代我做指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理母艦上的一切！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說母艦沒指揮官是不行的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我卻沒這個資格呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有資格現已不重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你盡量試試吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜是我身體不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經將如何去指揮母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,編成了一本書，你看過便明瞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這不行的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定做得到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.02,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你答應我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想我很快會康復的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我答應你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球聯邦軍雷比爾將軍接母艦消息後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便吩咐對母艦作出支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時，他也來到了歐洲的前線基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.37,0:04:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是希望基希莉亞及\N支持馬·克貝前進行敖德薩計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.04,0:04:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已是大戰前夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.05,0:04:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖只用一艘母艦向ZION軍攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.05,0:04:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但後方來說已夠他手忙腳亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過母艦現已被破壞的很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎是不能動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣想他便中了我們的計
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？瑪吉露達少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.74,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在關鍵只在乎於少尉的部隊他們\N能否盡快修理好White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.77,0:05:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！雷比爾將軍，我會全力以赴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.71,0:05:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一件東西我想你為我送去母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他們會認為是作實驗品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.39,0:05:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我還希望再增強GUNDAM的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增強GUNDAM的戰鬥力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面就是有關資料！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷比爾將軍，為何你如此看中母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.53,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班人還未編入正式軍籍內呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道可以找正規軍來作實驗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.21,0:05:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是參謀本部決定的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.21,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個情報很有用，不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還不知道如何強化GUNDAM呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，連艾少將在敖德薩作戰時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是有White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，叫連艾少將謹慎點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.66,0:06:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要適可宜止啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.73,0:06:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來聯邦軍已沒耐性等下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.70,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一戰，誰先動手就誰先敗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.67,0:06:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,林巴，派古夫及YS戰機各三架一起對付運輸機吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.37,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加些護衛機去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.20,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.91,0:07:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才雷比爾將軍那邊有電文來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已用計算機翻譯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽聽吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.71,0:07:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是雷比爾將軍，真的對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼遲才送補給物資來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.85,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待瑪吉露達少尉幫你們修理好母艦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.35,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以一起參加敖德薩計劃了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有...我附送了一架GUNDAM的零件來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望它可以增加GUNDAM的戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對你們所有人都抱很大期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍是只得一些門面說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本連敖德薩計劃何時開始也不知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,具體的事瑪吉露達...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...待瑪吉露達少尉來到便清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知是什麼GUNDAM的零件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是可以令阿姆羅更方便作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.05,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便真的太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.43,0:08:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,11時方向發現有一編隊戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來尚差少些便到達的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.40,0:08:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是ZION軍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得很奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.90,0:08:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們沒可能這麼快便找到來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各單位立即準備應戰，小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即發出求救訊號給雷比爾將軍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經發現了運輸機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面滿載貨物根本就飛不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.03,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很輕易便可轟下他們了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛收到運輸機的求救訊號！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是運輸機嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.38,0:08:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西北180公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦？得不到補給品便完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...運輸機一定要來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，立即去救運輸機吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.89,0:09:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅、隼人、凱出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡快去搶救瑪吉露達少尉的運輸機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，等一等！我要取消命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.51,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這樣我們會沒有戰機保護啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.01,0:09:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如敵軍再來那又怎應付？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要保留一些戰機才可！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你上核戰機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞中、隼人，上GUNDAM運輸機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即刻準備GUNDAM的零件！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.83,0:09:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱上鋼加農！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不喜歡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要處分我也沒辦法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.83,0:09:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，隊長將指揮權交給我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.33,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊，凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.87,0:10:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉送來了很多資源呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.38,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是是，雪拉小姐很會激勵人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.71,0:10:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM運輸機出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望敵人不會來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，你坐在指揮官位置上如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該要再冷靜一點吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看現在應叫大家全面戒備呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.69,0:10:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪吉露達少尉，你要加油支持著啊！
